<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Welcome to Our Service</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome, @Model.Name!</h1>
    <p>We are excited to have you onboard. Here's a summary of your information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> @Model.Email</li>
        <li><strong>Sign-up Date:</strong> @Model.SignUpDate.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We look forward to serving you.</p>
</body>
</html>
